Package: LINEMAP
Type: Package
Title: Lineage Simulation and Reconstruction from Barcode Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "LINEMAP", family = "Developers",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com")
Description: Tools for simulating lineage trees from transition matrices and
    reconstructing phylogenies from barcode sequence observations. The package
    includes probability-distance dictionary construction, distance matrix
    estimation, tree building wrappers, and tree comparison utilities.
